               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝṣṣǝw, Lectionary for the week (fols. 2ra-36ra)
 -
                     Blessing prayer (Barǝkännä ʾǝgziʾo… “Bless us, Lord…”: fols. 2ra-4rb
 -
                     Monday (sänuy): fols. 5ra-9ra
 - Tuesday (śälus): fols. 9rb-15rb
 -
                     Thursday (ḥamus): fols. 15rb-19va
 - Friday (ʾarb): fols. 19va-24vb
 -
                     Saturday (qadāmit): fols. 24vb-29vb
 - Sunday (ʾǝḥud): fols. 30ra-36ra
                     II) Maṣḥafa nǝfq “Book of the Assistant Priest” (fols. 36ra-48rb)
 I-1)
                     Prayer of oblation (fols. 36ra-37ra): excerpt from the Liturgy of Catechumen
                     (MQ, Śǝrʿatä qǝddase, ch. III, §§ 41-44). 
 I-2) Fǝtḥat za-wald “Absolution
                     of the Son” (fols. 37ra-39rb): excerpt from the Liturgy of Catechumen (MQ,
                     Śǝrʿatä qǝddase, ch. III, §§ 56-65).
 I-3) Concluding chant after the
                     reading from the Pauline Epistles (fols. 39rb-40rb): excerpt from the Liturgy
                     of the Word (MQ, Śǝrʿatä qǝddase, ch. III, §§ 132-135).
 I-4) Universal
                     prayer by the assistant priest (fols. 40rb-42ra): excerpt from the Liturgy of
                     the Word (MQ, Śǝrʿatä qǝddase, ch. III, §§ 194-209).
 I-5) Supplication for
                     peace, the hierarchy and the assembly (fols. 42ra-43ra): excerpt from the
                     Liturgy of the Word (MQ, Śǝrʿatä qǝddase, ch. IV, §§ 15-21).
 I-6) Prayer
                     of blessing of St Basil (fols. 43ra-44vb): excerpt from the Liturgy of the
                     Eucharist, Anaphora of the Apostles (MQ, Qǝddase za-ḥawāryāt, §§ 10-21).
                     I-7) Prayer of intercession following the imposition of the celebrant‘s hand
                     (fols. 44vb-48rb): excerpt from the Liturgy of the Eucharist, Anaphora of the
                     Apostles (MQ, Qǝddase za-ḥawāryāt, §§ 154-158)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
